# CIS hardening additional group policy for local gp (no domain)
# As part of CIS window server hardening process, additional gp template have to be downloaded.
# To apply policy on non domain joined pc
# Download the admx files/ folder from source
Change directory to C:\Windows\PolicyDefinitions\
# Copy the new admx and adml files to C:\Windows\PolicyDefinitions\ and C:\Windows\PolicyDefinitions\en-US respectively

